If I were rating on the food alone I would give it a 4 star. I enjoy the food served here. Unfortunately the service is subpar. The cashier was very rude. My wife asked if they had tea and the cashiers response was "Ya we do, I have no idea what kind though, it's over there you can go check it out" after ordering the tea the cashier handed my wife a steaming glass of water. We waited for our sandwiches, finished eating and it is STILL steaming, way too hot to even sip still.

